entries.femaleVariant: I dunno... just don't wanna. I'm worried... Yeah, I know there's no reason. Everyone does it. Yeah, I know.
But it just seems so wrong. Letting someone cut out a part of you...
How come I'm the only one who thinks it's weird? Yanking out your eye and shoving in a chunk of metal...
Hey, don't start, all right? What if I'm not the one who's gonked? Maybe the world's gonked!
Hah, yeah, I wish! But I can't. I'll be even more behind at work.
She said it was either a Kiroshi and a coprocessor, or my walking papers.
